---
title: Dilly Chicken and Orzo with Spinach and Feta
description: Classic Greek  flavours like feta, dill and lemon are featured in this heartwarming chicken and orzo dish. Here at the HelloFresh test kitchen we absolutely love dill, but feel free to use as much or as little as you like!
